.SH NAME
couchdb \- Apache CouchDB database server
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B couchdb
[\fIOPTION\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
The couchdb command runs the Apache CouchDB server.
.PP
Erlang inherits the environment of this command.
.PP
